{"tid":2306956,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"now記者真係完全唔做功課","createTime":"2020-11-30T23:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T05:04:10.000Z","uid":72476,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f4137d8575937b36b83bdb65f05ca966302a18","tid":2306956,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T23:19:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/sports/player?newsId=sp31542186481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp31542186481&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xGSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=34e5c00b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp31542186481&h=9697a5a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/sports/player?newsId=sp31542186481</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】曼聯新兵卡雲尼於周日聯賽大發神威，然而賽後有餘波，他涉於社交網絡展示帶有種族歧視的字眼，可能面臨停賽3場的處分。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯周日以3:2反勝修咸頓，據報指，直接與間接參與紅魔全部入球的卡雲尼（Edinson Cavani）因為在回應網民恭賀後，用上帶有種族歧視的字眼&ldquo;gracias negrito&rdquo;，意思是「黑棍」，有違英超反種族歧視的E3條例。英足總表明展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n雖然他得悉可能出現的惡果後，立時刪除帖文，然而英超條例具追溯力，他或因此被重罰停賽3場。去年，曼城前鋒賓納度施華因出了帶有種族歧視的帖文，即使刪除亦被罰停賽1場。<span class=\"red\">2011年，卡雲尼的烏拉圭攻擊拍檔蘇亞雷斯，並曾因為對曼聯的艾夫拿用上&ldquo;gracias negrito&rdquo;的字句而受罰。</span><br />\n<br />\n英超賽會於本季前發出防止種族歧視行為的指引，並表明球員一旦違例，最低刑罰是停賽3場。曼聯截至英超周日晚都未就事件發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Gracias&rdquo;即係&rdquo;thank you&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個記者唔做research直接當係歧視字句既一部份<br />\n心諗當年蘇七點解會同艾夫拿講gracias<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642d6fc4ad23d19492a639a3bfe6f0ab49c0b1bf","tid":2306956,"uid":306413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T02:34:06.000Z","msg":"唔係歧視既話人地而家英超就唔會查緊佢啦 傻閪"},{"pid":"558832609f87543c36c6